{
  "texts": [
    "See Supplementary Note 1 for more detailed extraction and sequencing methods.",
    "Chromium linked-read (10x Genomics) data were assembled with Supernova 152 (v1. 1.5).",
    "This assembly was used to seed the assembly of PacBio CLR data using DBG2OLC 153 (commit 1f7e752).",
    "An independent PacBio-only assembly was constructed with Canu 154 (v1.6-132-gf9284f8).",
    "These two assemblies were combined, or metassembled, using MUMmer 155 (v3.23) and quickmerge 156 (commit e4ea490) (Supplementary Fig. 1a)."
  ]
}